s the poster girl then that's quite the achievement,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"the poster girl\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the achievement\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am privileged to be in that position.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, I can go on and do what she did and bring home the gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinsonsmashed her own British record for two laps of the track at her last outing at the Diamond League in London earlier this month before relocating to the British team's pre-Olympic holding camp.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2025126562780795e-12, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}, {\"begin\": 1314, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999982305781, \"rank\": 1.7692390300612223e-09, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999487117761, \"rank\": 5.1183836330225394e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], 